                <p class="font-normal text-sm md:text-base text-center mb-10">Welcome to our Peer-to-Peer Car Sharing Web Application community! We are committed to providing a safe and inclusive platform for car sharing. To ensure that everyone feels welcome and respected, we have established the following Nondiscriminatory Terms and Policies:</p>
