                            <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500">Members of our community are prohibited from discriminating against others based on their race, ethnicity, gender, sexual orientation, religion, age, or any other personal characteristic. Discrimination includes but is not limited to refusing to rent a vehicle to someone based on their personal characteristics, using derogatory language towards someone, or treating someone unfairly based on their personal characteristics.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Term 40 -->
